Trinity::

She looked down and took her paw off his foot. "I'm sorry mister."
She turned and looked around.  She looked over and saw a small 
butterfly floating along on top of some grass.  She giggles and 
darted after it.  She jumped up and tried to catch it.  She wasn't 
paying attention and wandered off farther away from the others.
